Global Puff Food Extruder Market Insights
Puff Food Extruder Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Puff Food Extruder Market Overview
The global puff food extruder market size was valued at approximately USD 4.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to expand at a CAGR of 5.6% from 2025 to 2032. The market is driven by the increasing demand for ready-to-eat puffed snacks, as well as advancements in food processing technologies. Extruders are essential for the production of a variety of puffed snacks such as cereals, chips, and other snack foods, which are growing in popularity among consumers globally due to their convenience and taste. As such, manufacturers are adopting these technologies to meet the growing consumer demand. This increase in demand is being observed across both developed and emerging markets, contributing to the robust growth of the puff food extruder market.

